{"tid":2066874,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"啤梨：若共產黨政治手段夠高，俾你35+又如何呢？","createTime":"2020-06-16T14:54:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-16T15:28:12.000Z","uid":219007,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"9a4f2295faf08f1d8ef04ae54e7c7a2449d7f173","tid":2066874,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T14:54:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/N4jPrnVJg8o\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FN4jPrnVJg8o&d=St%2FdMm9ieZWtYGJEeV6aazDyw%2Fr9SRfH8QBX8OZV2FM%3D&h=3cf529a9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/N4jPrnVJg8o</a><br />\n<br />\n李怡講得啱<br />\n這八年內，我與我的朋友都試過晒俾人話係鬼<br />\n我而家少屌泛民係因為已經屌到費事再屌，老實講，你35+仲有乜嘢意義？？？<br />\n<br />\n如果共產黨政治手段夠高，俾你35+又如何呢？ 就憑你地35+可以做到啲咩？？係你地話「後生仔唔使送頭，我哋議會入邊抗爭吧」佢後生仔點解會繼續出嚟，係因為信你哋議會唔過。 但往往當我地批評你地嘅時候就俾你地話係分裂泛民。<br />\n<br />\n「黃毓民收共產黨錢」到今時今日仲有人講緊。證據呢？「有啲嘢唔需要證據嘅」 咁我夠可以話「泛民收共產黨錢」「劉細良之前喺建制入邊㗎，仲唔係收共產黨錢？」一樣冇證據架吹呀～<br />\n<br />\n呢啲陰謀論我盡量少講，劉細良仲話有D人持住眾人皆醉我獨醒嘅態度，劉細良你唔好同我嚟呢一套啦。 例如劉夢熊，我唔會評論佢以前做過啲乜嘢，只睇佢今日講嘅嘢，只要企喺香港人嘅一邊就係同路人！ <br />\n<br />\n一個袁弓夷，當然唔係劉細良同范國威鬧佢，你睇埋下面嗰班留言就知道，黃粉一樣都係眾人皆醉我獨醒嘅態度。<br />\n所以根本冇得團結。 我好多年前講過一番說話「我寧願比共產黨統治，都唔想比泛民統治」因為你呢班人仲衰過共產黨。"},{"pid":"5155fee56d50047b970174cbfad1235f61671260","tid":2066874,"uid":48083,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T14:56:08.000Z","msg":"哩句其實萬能key嚟<br />\n夠高既話任何手段都冇用添<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1727aa295cb1a5b7721eecd52102f845db49945a","tid":2066874,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T14:57:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"338c3fee582ada5d33bd2c0de08b523d0347453c","tid":2066874,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5155fee56d50047b970174cbfad1235f61671260","tid":2066874,"uid":48083,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T14:56:08.000Z","msg":"哩句其實萬能key嚟<br />\n夠高既話任何手段都冇用添<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T15:03:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n 夠高70都冇用"},{"pid":"bc4c215165f2c32cf7b3799cef0c175a8d84e9c4","tid":2066874,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"338c3fee582ada5d33bd2c0de08b523d0347453c","tid":2066874,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5155fee56d50047b970174cbfad1235f61671260","tid":2066874,"uid":48083,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T14:56:08.000Z","msg":"哩句其實萬能key嚟<br />\n夠高既話任何手段都冇用添<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T15:03:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n 夠高70都冇用"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T15:05:16.000Z","msg":"最高嗰個就係叫你放棄，<br />\n做乜都冇用嗰個。"},{"pid":"a8fa42938aed021e761dae07c34bdfcea0efb01a","tid":2066874,"uid":343361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T15:14:41.000Z","msg":"佢都跪咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4126b4b59789faa0f0dcee4d0701f91c2c109018","tid":2066874,"uid":235152,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T15:28:12.000Z","msg":"佢有一半無講錯如果35過黃碧雲級數入去的確同廢一撚樣<br />\n民主黨同其他功能組別表明未必攬炒咁到時可以點<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}